headline: Why First Solar (FSLR) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of solar panel manufacturer First Solar (NASDAQ:FSLR) jumped 3.3% in the morning session after Jefferies raised its price target on the stock to $260 from $212, citing a positive outlook for the company.
